# Shared Brief — Session 044 Path OC Deliberation

This brief is read in common by all four perspectives. Each perspective additionally receives a role-specific stance when convened (see §5 below). The brief is the **neutral ground**: shared question set, shared reading guidance, shared output format, shared reminders. Role-specific framing (what lens to apply) lives in §5.

## 0. Operator ratification (recorded verbatim)

The session-open assessment `00-assessment.md` halted at §9 for operator ratification of the deliberation shape. The operator's response:

> R1 as proposed. R2 alternative: Gemini is a weaker reasoning model at present. You should consider setting the two non-Claude perspectives to both be codex. R3: Drop Q5 as three-family is constrained by the reasoning agents we have access to, at present just Claude and Codex, Gemini can only be used for minor deliberations. R4: Convene in this session.

**Resolved shape**:
