- **R2 operator-revised**: both non-Claude perspectives are Codex/GPT (neither the assessment-proposed Option A [P3=Gemini, P4=GPT] nor Option B [P3=GPT, P4=Gemini]). P3 Outsider = Codex/GPT; P4 Cross-Family Reviewer = Codex/GPT. Rationale: Gemini is operationally weaker at substantive reasoning at present and is restricted to minor deliberations. Three-family convening (Claude + Gemini + Codex) is the ideal shape but is operationally constrained for this substantive deliberation; operator has updated the convening preference to reflect this.
