2. **Three-perspective Claude-only deliberation**. Rejected: operator explicitly requested "at least one non-Claude lineage"; this session is also the operator-identified opportunity to cast §5.6 observational data point on vindication side; cross-family participation is required by both operator direction and standing minority warrant.

