5. **Combine with a §6.2 audit shape**. Rejected: §6.2 audit shapes are structured around post-v-bump quality checks (S029 / S034 / S037), not around substantive meta-questions about path-selection. Combining would conflate verification work with generative work and is likely to produce weaker output on both.

